id: hac-l25p
title: Auto-release dry run omits pm-changelog installation on clean runners
description: "The exact-master non-publishing Auto Release dispatch fails on a clean GitHub runner because scripts/release/auto-release.mjs skips installLatestChangelog() when --dry-run is set, then invokes an unavailable pm changelog command."
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 0
tags[7]: automation,changelog,dry-run,github-actions,pm-changelog,production-follow-up,release
created_at: "2026-07-21T21:11:50.143Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-21T21:11:57.740Z"
deadline: "2026-07-22T21:11:50.143Z"
assignee: codex-root
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 45
acceptance_criteria: "A clean-runner workflow_dispatch with dry_run=true and allow_same_day_release=true installs the latest pm-changelog, generates the candidate changelog, completes all release gates, and does not commit, tag, push, or publish"
definition_of_ready: Exact failed workflow job log identifies Unknown command changelog after the dry-run-only installation branch
goal: lossless-automatic-releases
objective: clean-runner-dry-run-parity
value: Keep the non-publishing release rehearsal trustworthy on clean infrastructure.
impact: Prevents false release failures and ensures scheduled release prerequisites are exercised before publication.
outcome: Hosted auto-release dry runs complete end to end while preserving their no-publish contract.
why_now: Exact final master proof run 29868743104 exposed the clean-runner gap.
parent: hac-wwsi
reviewer: unbraind
risk: high
confidence: high
reporter: codex-root
severity: high
environment: GitHub Actions Auto Release workflow_dispatch on a clean ubuntu runner
repro_steps: "Dispatch auto-release.yml on master with push=false, dry_run=true, allow_same_day_release=true; observe scripts/release/auto-release.mjs invoke pm changelog without first installing pm-changelog."
expected_result: Dry-run and publishing modes both provision the latest changelog generator before generating release notes.
actual_result: Dry-run mode skips installLatestChangelog and fails with Unknown command changelog.
affected_version: 2026.7.21-2
component: release-automation
regression: false
customer_impact: No publication occurred; maintainers cannot rely on the hosted dry-run rehearsal.
